Since version 0.3.9, EffecTV supports only vloopback-0.91 or later. Older
version doesn't work correctly without a hack, and the latest vloopback module
fixes the problem. The latest vloopback can be downloaded from:

http://www.lavrsen.dk/twiki/bin/view/Motion/VideoFourLinuxLoopbackDevice

If you use Linux kernel 2.6.x, you should download version 0.93-snap1 or later.
